WEBVTT

00:00:01.105 --> 00:00:03.865
I think Dr. Puth was trying
to avenge Puifai.

00:00:03.945 --> 00:00:05.945
But taking the body with him?

00:00:06.025 --> 00:00:07.625
Don't you think
that's a bit too psychotic?

00:00:08.385 --> 00:00:09.745
Choose.

00:00:09.825 --> 00:00:11.265
Who are you going to save?

00:00:11.345 --> 00:00:12.265
Champ?

00:00:13.345 --> 00:00:14.505
Or Cherreen?

00:00:14.585 --> 00:00:16.945
I'm not choosing!
I'm not choosing anyone to die.

00:00:17.025 --> 00:00:19.185
I'll go first. You follow.

00:00:19.265 --> 00:00:21.225
You've been removed from the case.

00:00:21.305 --> 00:00:22.145
Wait for me.

00:00:22.745 --> 00:00:23.705
It's okay.

00:00:25.185 --> 00:00:27.505
No matter what,
I still have you by my side.

00:00:28.105 --> 00:00:30.225
I love you, Jade.

00:00:30.305 --> 00:00:31.265
Kamin.

00:00:31.345 --> 00:00:32.864
Kamin!

00:01:12.625 --> 00:01:13.905
Fai, what are you doing?

00:01:13.985 --> 00:01:16.025
Can you please let me go, Puth?

00:01:25.105 --> 00:01:26.625
No.

00:01:26.705 --> 00:01:27.945
Don't do this.

00:01:31.625 --> 00:01:33.905
You're not the one who deserves to die.

00:01:35.025 --> 00:01:37.385
They are.

00:01:38.345 --> 00:01:40.505
Then what do you want me to do?

00:01:41.105 --> 00:01:43.105
I can't report this to the police.

00:01:43.745 --> 00:01:45.905
I can't tell anyone about it.

00:01:46.545 --> 00:01:49.785
Right now, my life is worthless.

00:01:52.265 --> 00:01:54.265
My life was worthless too

00:01:58.585 --> 00:02:00.505
until I found you.

00:02:02.345 --> 00:02:04.905
If you think you're worthless,

00:02:06.545 --> 00:02:08.545
then let's be worthless together.

00:02:11.985 --> 00:02:13.865
I'll help you.

00:03:45.545 --> 00:03:46.945
Puifai.

00:03:50.185 --> 00:03:52.065
You're not dead?

00:03:53.945 --> 00:03:55.825
So what's your choice, Jay?

00:03:58.385 --> 00:04:00.185
So everything that's happened
was your doing?

00:04:02.465 --> 00:04:03.865
Did you kill all of our friends?

00:04:03.945 --> 00:04:06.425
Jay, why would you say
something like that?

00:04:06.505 --> 00:04:08.625
I only sent our friends home…

00:04:11.705 --> 00:04:13.145
in hell.

00:04:13.985 --> 00:04:15.465
Did you have to go this far and kill them?

00:04:16.425 --> 00:04:18.665
Did they do something that wrong?

00:04:19.465 --> 00:04:22.225
If you want to know that badly,
Jay, then choose.

00:04:23.785 --> 00:04:25.025
I won't choose!

00:04:26.265 --> 00:04:28.265
That's fine.

00:04:28.905 --> 00:04:30.945
Then let them both die.

00:04:31.865 --> 00:04:34.145
- Don't!
- This is Puifai's house.

00:04:34.225 --> 00:04:36.505
She bought it six months
before the murder happened.

00:04:36.585 --> 00:04:38.025
Six months?

00:04:38.985 --> 00:04:41.025
That was when Puifai was still pregnant.

00:04:42.105 --> 00:04:43.985
Or was all of this part of Puifai's plan?

00:04:44.585 --> 00:04:46.585
Tell Yu and Lee
to send me Kamin's location.

00:04:46.665 --> 00:04:49.425
Inspector Kamin's car just left
the main road a few minutes ago.

00:04:50.345 --> 00:04:51.505
Damn it!

00:04:57.585 --> 00:04:58.585
Don't!

00:05:01.305 --> 00:05:02.705
I've chosen! Truth!

00:05:02.785 --> 00:05:04.905
I'll tell you everything myself.

00:05:14.225 --> 00:05:15.425
Jay.

00:05:18.505 --> 00:05:20.705
You knew from the beginning

00:05:22.625 --> 00:05:25.145
that Tar was going to rape me

00:05:27.105 --> 00:05:30.345
as part of Champ's plan
to make me his girlfriend, didn't you?

00:05:34.225 --> 00:05:35.825
You also knew

00:05:37.345 --> 00:05:39.665
that Bell told Cherreen and Champ

00:05:39.745 --> 00:05:42.465
about my pregnancy, right?

00:05:43.665 --> 00:05:45.665
That's why they dragged me
to get an abortion.

00:05:45.745 --> 00:05:47.465
I didn't know.

00:05:47.545 --> 00:05:49.265
I really didn't know, Puifai!

00:05:49.345 --> 00:05:51.785
You never told me anything.

00:05:51.865 --> 00:05:54.265
I could've been the baby's father!

00:05:57.745 --> 00:05:59.665
But you knew

00:06:00.665 --> 00:06:03.185
they planned to drug me
from the start, didn't you?

00:06:04.785 --> 00:06:06.625
You didn't stop them

00:06:08.025 --> 00:06:10.745
because you were afraid of
this asshole Champ.

00:06:12.265 --> 00:06:14.505
You must've known

00:06:14.585 --> 00:06:16.585
that Time and Tonkla

00:06:17.425 --> 00:06:22.265
secretly recorded me, Bell, and Cherreen
and sold the clips online.

00:06:26.145 --> 00:06:28.185
You knew everything, Jay,

00:06:30.345 --> 00:06:32.305
but you never helped me.

00:06:32.385 --> 00:06:35.185
I knew. I'm sorry.

00:06:35.945 --> 00:06:38.185
I knew the truth.

00:06:39.545 --> 00:06:41.665
I pretended nothing happened

00:06:43.745 --> 00:06:46.105
because I thought
there was nothing I could do.

00:06:49.345 --> 00:06:51.185
Wrong answer, Jay.

00:06:51.985 --> 00:06:54.145
You could've done something.

00:06:54.225 --> 00:06:55.785
You just weren't brave enough.

00:06:59.025 --> 00:07:03.465
I once believed
you would definitely help me.

00:07:04.545 --> 00:07:06.105
But I was wrong.

00:07:08.105 --> 00:07:11.905
So today, if you want to survive,

00:07:13.225 --> 00:07:14.705
you should choose.

00:07:14.785 --> 00:07:17.385
Who will die in your place?

00:07:18.305 --> 00:07:19.945
Champ

00:07:22.345 --> 00:07:23.705
or Cherreen?

00:07:26.065 --> 00:07:28.025
You want me to choose
someone to die in my place?

00:07:28.105 --> 00:07:29.505
Are you out of your mind?

00:07:29.585 --> 00:07:31.865
- I won't choose!
- Then your game is over.

00:07:32.945 --> 00:07:34.985
You can watch them die
over and over again.

00:08:41.225 --> 00:08:42.865
Champ.

00:08:42.945 --> 00:08:44.505
Champ!

00:08:46.665 --> 00:08:48.305
Where is this place?

00:08:51.905 --> 00:08:53.425
Shit.

00:08:53.505 --> 00:08:55.185
Where the hell are we?

00:08:56.305 --> 00:08:58.105
Who caught us?

00:08:59.305 --> 00:09:03.065
Hey, is anyone out there?

00:09:03.145 --> 00:09:04.625
Hey!

00:09:05.425 --> 00:09:07.785
Asshole! Do you know who I am?

00:09:07.865 --> 00:09:09.465
Hey, let me go!

00:09:11.425 --> 00:09:12.945
Hey!

00:09:15.785 --> 00:09:16.665
Shit!

00:09:16.745 --> 00:09:18.585
DRUG CHERREEN AND BRING HER
TO THE LOCATION I SENT

00:09:18.665 --> 00:09:19.945
DON'T LET ANYONE KNOW AND YOU'LL SURVIVE

00:09:22.105 --> 00:09:23.625
Champ, you already got the letter?

00:09:25.825 --> 00:09:27.505
You said you didn't.

00:09:31.145 --> 00:09:33.905
Well, you're no different.

00:09:33.985 --> 00:09:35.465
You said you only got the Truth one.

00:09:36.265 --> 00:09:39.745
At least I told you I got the letter!

00:09:40.985 --> 00:09:45.145
It's nice to see you fighting like this.

00:09:46.385 --> 00:09:48.905
I thought you were only
in love with each other.

00:09:49.985 --> 00:09:51.705
Puifai.

00:09:55.865 --> 00:09:59.705
That's the doctor
who examined Puifai's body.

00:10:01.625 --> 00:10:04.505
What the hell did you do?

00:10:04.585 --> 00:10:05.545
Did you fake your death?

00:10:05.625 --> 00:10:11.025
You want to know how all
the disgusting shit you did led to this?

00:10:12.985 --> 00:10:14.985
But I'm done talking to you.

00:10:16.065 --> 00:10:20.425
So I'll let my boyfriend
explain it instead.

00:10:21.105 --> 00:10:22.825
Is that okay, babe?

00:10:22.905 --> 00:10:24.905
Of course, babe.

00:10:30.945 --> 00:10:34.625
The anesthesia should last a while longer.
They shouldn't wake up yet.

00:10:34.705 --> 00:10:39.265
Potassium chloride will make your heart
appear to have stopped.

00:10:39.345 --> 00:10:42.025
If everything goes as planned,

00:10:42.105 --> 00:10:45.025
I can inject the antidote
and start dialysis in time.

00:10:45.105 --> 00:10:49.465
But I'm not sure your body can handle it.

00:10:49.545 --> 00:10:53.145
I believe you'll bring me back, Puth.

00:10:53.865 --> 00:10:56.385
You can still change your mind.

00:10:57.545 --> 00:11:01.065
If I die, then I die.

00:11:03.745 --> 00:11:06.105
But if I survive and come back,

00:11:08.465 --> 00:11:12.785
every single one of them must die.

00:11:16.425 --> 00:11:18.625
This is the dare I've chosen.

00:11:34.265 --> 00:11:36.785
Did you really have to do
all this to us, Fai?

00:11:39.745 --> 00:11:43.785
You wanted revenge so badly
that you killed your own friends?

00:11:45.305 --> 00:11:46.585
Isn't this too much?

00:11:46.665 --> 00:11:48.465
Too much?

00:11:49.305 --> 00:11:51.985
Have you even thought about
what you did to me?

00:11:55.225 --> 00:11:59.825
What you did made me feel like
I was dead inside.

00:12:01.145 --> 00:12:02.465
But all of us…

00:12:06.025 --> 00:12:07.945
were really worried about you.

00:12:10.305 --> 00:12:11.145
Bullshit.

00:12:13.345 --> 00:12:17.345
You were so worried that
you two slept together behind my back?

00:12:22.145 --> 00:12:24.065
And weren't you the one

00:12:24.145 --> 00:12:28.385
who told Bell
you wanted me to die quickly?

00:12:34.585 --> 00:12:36.145
Champ.

00:12:36.225 --> 00:12:39.225
When I almost died from bleeding
after the abortion,

00:12:40.625 --> 00:12:43.305
you didn't care about me at all.

00:12:59.305 --> 00:13:00.705
Fai.

00:13:08.425 --> 00:13:09.865
We're sorry.

00:13:13.385 --> 00:13:15.345
Please let us go.

00:13:15.425 --> 00:13:18.505
We can talk this out calmly, okay?

00:13:19.025 --> 00:13:20.825
We'll do anything.

00:13:25.585 --> 00:13:27.025
Sure.

00:13:34.865 --> 00:13:36.945
Do you really think I'd answer like that?

00:13:38.945 --> 00:13:41.065
I don't want your fucking truth anymore.

00:13:41.585 --> 00:13:43.385
I choose dare.

00:13:44.145 --> 00:13:46.665
Talk it out and decide

00:13:46.745 --> 00:13:52.265
who gets to live
and who gets to die today.

00:13:59.705 --> 00:14:00.905
You've gone crazy. Stop it.

00:14:01.785 --> 00:14:04.305
You're too good
to be doing something like this.

00:14:04.905 --> 00:14:09.705
Cherreen, if you really thought
I was a good person,

00:14:09.785 --> 00:14:11.425
why did you do this to me?

00:14:12.745 --> 00:14:14.145
You bitch!

00:14:14.225 --> 00:14:17.305
Let me out right now.
I'm not playing this shit!

00:14:19.025 --> 00:14:20.225
Jay.

00:14:21.585 --> 00:14:24.385
Jay, wake up.

00:14:28.345 --> 00:14:29.305
Don't fall asleep yet.

00:14:31.265 --> 00:14:35.745
That doctor and Puifai
are about to kill Cherreen and Champ.

00:14:35.825 --> 00:14:37.585
Puifai?

00:14:37.665 --> 00:14:40.665
Are you sure you don't want to play?

00:14:51.105 --> 00:14:52.665
They're upstairs.

00:14:52.745 --> 00:14:54.265
Go help them first.

00:14:55.465 --> 00:14:56.505
Champ.

00:15:04.905 --> 00:15:06.625
I'm not dying.

00:15:07.825 --> 00:15:09.785
If Fai wants to play a game,

00:15:10.705 --> 00:15:12.145
I'm going to survive.

00:15:12.225 --> 00:15:13.705
You bastard!

00:15:17.225 --> 00:15:18.945
Woo-hoo!

00:15:19.025 --> 00:15:20.945
This is getting more fun.

00:15:21.625 --> 00:15:24.905
But it will be even more fun
if things are fair.

00:15:26.665 --> 00:15:28.705
Please go help them first.
I'm begging you.

00:15:34.385 --> 00:15:35.305
Do your best.

00:15:48.865 --> 00:15:50.385
I'll go check downstairs.

00:15:50.465 --> 00:15:52.625
- You wait here.
- Thank you.

00:16:25.145 --> 00:16:27.825
Champ, after this is over,

00:16:27.905 --> 00:16:29.945
your dad's sending you
to study abroad, right?

00:16:30.025 --> 00:16:34.185
Why don't you just end this
and start a new life?

00:16:35.985 --> 00:16:37.505
As for you, Cherreen,

00:16:37.585 --> 00:16:41.945
a woman like you doesn't need Champ
to survive anyway.

00:16:43.945 --> 00:16:46.505
Champ, don't listen to her.

00:16:46.585 --> 00:16:50.305
Do you really think she'll let you go
after killing me?

00:16:51.025 --> 00:16:55.265
At least I still have a chance to survive.

00:16:57.305 --> 00:16:58.425
Don't, Champ!

00:16:58.505 --> 00:16:59.385
Champ!

00:17:36.865 --> 00:17:38.905
There's blood, Cher!

00:17:52.265 --> 00:17:54.185
Let's stop this, Champ. Enough already.

00:18:35.785 --> 00:18:37.905
What should we do next, boss?

00:18:37.985 --> 00:18:40.265
There are two of them.

00:18:40.345 --> 00:18:43.665
We need a decoy to split them up.

00:18:49.865 --> 00:18:51.305
Ouch!

00:18:51.385 --> 00:18:53.025
Shit.

00:19:00.265 --> 00:19:01.465
Cher!

00:19:09.585 --> 00:19:11.385
This is the police.

00:19:11.465 --> 00:19:13.945
It's all over, Puifai.

00:19:15.065 --> 00:19:17.705
Champ, Cherreen, stop right now.

00:19:18.865 --> 00:19:22.625
No matter how hard you fight,
the only real winner is Puifai.

00:19:44.465 --> 00:19:46.265
I just found out that

00:19:47.625 --> 00:19:50.985
you like playing
hide-and-seek too, Officer.

00:19:56.785 --> 00:20:00.465
Your truth-or-dare game is over.

00:20:01.545 --> 00:20:02.985
The culprit's been found.

00:20:07.225 --> 00:20:09.505
I don't like this game, though.

00:20:10.345 --> 00:20:13.225
Why don't we switch to
"This or That" instead?

00:20:14.865 --> 00:20:16.665
You give two options,

00:20:17.745 --> 00:20:19.785
and the other person just chooses.

00:20:26.705 --> 00:20:30.545
Between your heart and your head,

00:20:32.185 --> 00:20:33.865
where do you want me to put the bullet?

00:20:35.185 --> 00:20:36.585
My head, please.

00:20:40.105 --> 00:20:42.265
There's still a chance I might survive.

00:20:43.705 --> 00:20:47.825
If it's my heart,
I'd probably die right away.

00:20:53.385 --> 00:20:56.865
But now it's Champ's and Cherreen's turn.

00:21:04.145 --> 00:21:05.425
Don't!

00:21:14.105 --> 00:21:16.025
Now it's my turn.

00:21:19.145 --> 00:21:21.225
Jay, your younger brother,

00:21:23.905 --> 00:21:25.225
or Inspector Kamin?

00:21:28.905 --> 00:21:30.945
Who will you choose to save?

00:21:31.745 --> 00:21:33.505
What the hell are you going to do?

00:21:43.145 --> 00:21:44.625
Choose.

00:21:45.745 --> 00:21:47.185
Don't ask.

00:21:49.425 --> 00:21:54.425
But if you're curious,
I'll explain it out of kindness.

00:21:54.505 --> 00:21:59.385
The bottle in my hand contains
liquid oxygen.

00:22:00.945 --> 00:22:06.385
If it touches the aluminum powder here,

00:22:08.705 --> 00:22:10.265
it goes boom!

00:22:10.345 --> 00:22:12.225
I won.

00:22:12.305 --> 00:22:13.305
What about our deal?

00:22:13.385 --> 00:22:15.665
Okay, as promised.

00:22:28.305 --> 00:22:30.265
Put it down!

00:22:30.865 --> 00:22:35.545
You're no fun at all, Captain.

00:22:35.625 --> 00:22:36.785
Just choose already!

00:22:37.905 --> 00:22:40.385
Jay, who's on the verge of dying,

00:22:40.465 --> 00:22:42.145
or Inspector Kamin?

00:22:44.225 --> 00:22:45.465
Choose!

00:22:47.385 --> 00:22:48.825
Shit!

00:22:53.345 --> 00:22:54.585
Put it down!

00:22:59.505 --> 00:23:00.625
What the hell is this?

00:23:13.865 --> 00:23:15.465
Why do I have to choose…

00:23:16.985 --> 00:23:18.585
when I can save both of them?

00:23:26.345 --> 00:23:28.825
I won the game, so let me go.

00:23:28.905 --> 00:23:30.985
Do you really think
I want to see your face that much?

00:23:31.065 --> 00:23:32.625
I'll let you go,

00:23:33.545 --> 00:23:36.665
but not in good shape, I guess.

00:23:37.185 --> 00:23:38.465
Do you think you'll survive?

00:23:41.465 --> 00:23:42.705
Then we'll die together!

00:23:46.305 --> 00:23:48.185
- Fai, don't!
- Puifai!

00:23:49.585 --> 00:23:50.945
Think carefully.

00:23:51.665 --> 00:23:53.265
Don't do this.

00:23:55.025 --> 00:23:57.065
Your mother loves you very much.

00:24:00.225 --> 00:24:01.905
Jay, sit down first.

00:24:04.105 --> 00:24:06.185
Press on the wound. Keep pressing it.

00:24:07.025 --> 00:24:08.785
Ouch.

00:24:09.305 --> 00:24:11.225
Go help Kamin first.

00:24:12.825 --> 00:24:13.785
I'm okay.

00:24:13.865 --> 00:24:15.625
Promise me you won't fall asleep.

00:24:15.705 --> 00:24:17.105
Don't fall asleep, Jay.

00:24:17.185 --> 00:24:18.825
Don't fall asleep.

00:24:18.905 --> 00:24:20.305
Don't fall asleep!

00:24:20.385 --> 00:24:23.505
Yes, calm down, Fai.

00:24:23.585 --> 00:24:25.305
Take a deep breath.

00:24:25.385 --> 00:24:27.025
Think about your mother.

00:24:27.105 --> 00:24:28.065
Okay?

00:24:28.145 --> 00:24:31.345
Calm down and think about your mother.

00:24:32.945 --> 00:24:34.265
Kamin!

00:24:34.345 --> 00:24:35.905
- Screw you!
- Don't!

00:24:42.545 --> 00:24:45.425
Officer, I'm ready.

00:24:45.945 --> 00:24:48.425
Just seeing that bastard Champ like this

00:24:49.385 --> 00:24:52.105
is worth going to prison for.

00:25:48.825 --> 00:25:50.705
In the end,

00:25:51.985 --> 00:25:53.785
no one wins.

00:25:57.625 --> 00:25:59.225
Everyone loses.

00:26:00.865 --> 00:26:02.585
We do too.

00:26:09.785 --> 00:26:11.425
If we can't hold hands,

00:26:15.825 --> 00:26:17.465
then let's hug instead.

00:26:28.105 --> 00:26:32.025
What kind of idiot escapes the hospital
just to end up back in one?

00:26:32.105 --> 00:26:35.025
It's good that it wasn't worse.

00:26:35.105 --> 00:26:38.985
I heard Puth has third-degree burns.

00:26:39.065 --> 00:26:40.825
He has to stay in a sterile room

00:26:41.825 --> 00:26:43.225
and can't be exposed to air at all.

00:26:45.185 --> 00:26:47.985
As for Champ, he's still in surgery.

00:26:48.065 --> 00:26:50.505
They said his nerves are dead

00:26:51.505 --> 00:26:52.745
and probably can't be fixed.

00:26:54.745 --> 00:26:56.745
But even if both of them survive,

00:26:57.785 --> 00:26:59.625
they'll end up in prison anyway.

00:27:06.025 --> 00:27:07.505
Let Jay rest.

00:27:08.545 --> 00:27:10.025
We need rest too.

00:27:16.785 --> 00:27:18.865
Speaking of rest…

00:27:18.945 --> 00:27:21.105
We just closed a case this big,

00:27:22.225 --> 00:27:23.785
shouldn't we take a break?

00:27:25.745 --> 00:27:29.985
The bigger the case,
the more paperwork there is to clear.

00:27:30.065 --> 00:27:31.265
Oh no.

00:27:31.345 --> 00:27:34.025
I was planning to take you
on a trip out of town.

00:27:35.505 --> 00:27:37.065
Too bad.

00:27:37.585 --> 00:27:40.305
But actually,

00:27:40.985 --> 00:27:44.185
we could let Lieutenant Ken
and Lieutenant Prai handle the paperwork.

00:27:46.345 --> 00:27:47.825
That's true.

00:27:49.425 --> 00:27:51.265
Then…

00:27:52.265 --> 00:27:55.065
Let's go on a trip, babe.

00:28:02.305 --> 00:28:03.825
What did you just call me?

00:28:03.905 --> 00:28:05.785
Babe.

00:28:05.865 --> 00:28:07.505
Why?

00:28:07.585 --> 00:28:08.825
Don't you like it?

00:28:09.545 --> 00:28:11.225
Call me whatever you want.

00:28:14.465 --> 00:28:17.465
Then I'll call you babe.

00:29:00.745 --> 00:29:04.505
Wow, the view is amazing.

00:29:05.945 --> 00:29:07.425
Of course it is.

00:29:07.505 --> 00:29:09.345
Look at who chose the place.

00:29:11.025 --> 00:29:12.865
Come to think of it,

00:29:12.945 --> 00:29:15.985
it's been a long time
since I stayed somewhere like this.

00:29:16.065 --> 00:29:17.905
Thanks for inviting me.

00:29:17.985 --> 00:29:21.665
This is my way of saying thank you
for helping close that big case,

00:29:22.225 --> 00:29:24.865
and for helping with the commander too.

00:29:27.265 --> 00:29:29.345
If we're talking about that,

00:29:33.465 --> 00:29:36.425
then welcome back officially, Inspector.

00:29:47.745 --> 00:29:49.345
Why did you buy so many things?

00:29:50.025 --> 00:29:52.025
Well, if we're going on
an outing like this,

00:29:52.105 --> 00:29:53.825
we need some activities.

00:29:53.905 --> 00:29:56.985
Are you ready for the mission, officer?

00:30:11.585 --> 00:30:12.745
He's here.

00:30:13.345 --> 00:30:16.505
I'll make my special BBQ sauce for you.

00:30:17.865 --> 00:30:21.745
But since we're at the beach,
don't forget the seafood dipping sauce.

00:30:21.825 --> 00:30:22.825
Sure.

00:30:23.465 --> 00:30:26.185
And you, marinate the meat.

00:30:26.265 --> 00:30:28.305
Why does it have to be me?

00:30:28.985 --> 00:30:30.705
Seriously?

00:30:31.345 --> 00:30:32.825
You want me to marinate it myself?

00:30:34.265 --> 00:30:35.745
Fine, Inspector.

00:30:37.065 --> 00:30:39.145
I'll do whatever you order.

00:31:05.465 --> 00:31:07.665
They're making the salt
way too sweet already.

00:31:27.705 --> 00:31:29.265
Try it.

00:31:29.345 --> 00:31:33.265
Wow, it looks so good.
You're lucky as hell, Jade.

00:31:34.385 --> 00:31:35.225
Can I try some?

00:31:45.065 --> 00:31:46.745
I salute you, Chef.

00:31:47.345 --> 00:31:50.185
It's really good.
Can you let Yu be your disciple?

00:31:51.225 --> 00:31:52.665
This is just the sauce.

00:31:52.745 --> 00:31:53.985
You have to try the meat.

00:31:57.785 --> 00:31:59.145
So?

00:32:04.625 --> 00:32:06.945
Kamin, quit the police force already.

00:32:08.065 --> 00:32:08.905
Why?

00:32:08.985 --> 00:32:11.345
Open a restaurant.
You'd make way more money.

00:32:11.425 --> 00:32:13.185
Give it a try.

00:32:13.265 --> 00:32:15.505
Oh, I forgot to tell you.

00:32:15.585 --> 00:32:18.225
My mom owns a restaurant in the U.S.

00:32:18.305 --> 00:32:19.985
This is her recipe.

00:32:21.465 --> 00:32:23.145
You never told me that.

00:32:23.225 --> 00:32:26.905
When I first transferred here,
the cases were a mess.

00:32:26.985 --> 00:32:29.305
I never really had the chance
to talk about it.

00:32:29.985 --> 00:32:33.185
I'm jealous of Jade.
He must get to eat good food every day.

00:32:33.265 --> 00:32:35.225
But before this,
all I had was rice porridge

00:32:35.305 --> 00:32:37.505
and grilled chicken with sticky rice.

00:32:41.745 --> 00:32:43.265
Do you want some shellfish?

00:33:32.465 --> 00:33:33.705
You know,

00:33:33.785 --> 00:33:37.385
I actually have a long checklist
of things I want to do with you.

00:33:37.905 --> 00:33:39.625
This is one of them.

00:33:40.185 --> 00:33:42.065
Coming to the beach with you.

00:33:46.985 --> 00:33:48.505
Is there more?

00:33:52.065 --> 00:33:53.185
Hiking together.

00:33:54.025 --> 00:33:55.745
Going shooting together.

00:33:56.785 --> 00:33:58.465
Traveling abroad together.

00:33:59.025 --> 00:34:00.665
Raising a dog or a cat.

00:34:01.705 --> 00:34:05.025
And I'll take you out on dates
in many places.

00:34:05.105 --> 00:34:06.865
Okay?

00:34:06.945 --> 00:34:08.705
And most importantly,

00:34:09.304 --> 00:34:10.545
I'll take you to meet my mom.

00:34:11.945 --> 00:34:13.784
Meet your mom already?

00:34:18.304 --> 00:34:22.304
It looks like I need my own checklist too.

00:34:28.545 --> 00:34:32.304
I actually have one thing on it already.

00:34:36.625 --> 00:34:37.585
Let's go, okay?

00:34:59.625 --> 00:35:00.665
Where's your checklist?

00:35:32.105 --> 00:35:33.505
Right here.

00:35:34.225 --> 00:35:35.945
This is my checklist.

00:35:38.345 --> 00:35:43.105
Doing something like this
with the person I love, by the sea.

00:35:43.785 --> 00:35:46.305
Then you'll need to add more
to your checklist.

00:35:47.625 --> 00:35:52.585
You'll be doing this
with the person you love in many places.

00:36:02.825 --> 00:36:08.265
Thank you for coming into my life
and completing it, Jade.

00:36:09.465 --> 00:36:15.705
You showed me how good it feels
to have someone I love by my side.

00:36:20.745 --> 00:36:22.705
I should be the one thanking you.

00:36:25.185 --> 00:36:27.345
Before you came into my life,

00:36:29.025 --> 00:36:31.065
I was just getting by day to day.

00:36:33.745 --> 00:36:35.265
But now…

00:36:38.105 --> 00:36:41.345
my future feels much clearer.

00:36:43.225 --> 00:36:45.505
You gave my life meaning.

00:36:49.305 --> 00:36:51.665
At your service.

00:36:51.745 --> 00:36:53.545
I love you,

00:36:54.825 --> 00:36:57.025
my Kamin.

00:36:59.105 --> 00:37:00.985
I love you,

00:37:01.065 --> 00:37:02.785
my Jade.

00:37:07.065 --> 00:37:08.705
I love you,

00:37:10.265 --> 00:37:12.625
MJ.

00:37:46.665 --> 00:37:48.665
You disappeared for so long.

00:37:48.745 --> 00:37:50.545
Were you investigating
a bedroom case or something?

00:37:52.065 --> 00:37:53.705
You talk nonsense,

00:37:54.345 --> 00:37:57.105
but it suits you as a top detective.

00:38:00.545 --> 00:38:04.745
Thank you, everyone,
for supporting us since day one.

00:38:04.825 --> 00:38:07.585
We're one team now.

00:38:07.665 --> 00:38:10.865
If you need anything from now on,
just tell me.

00:38:10.945 --> 00:38:13.345
- Same here.
- Come on!

00:38:13.425 --> 00:38:16.105
We're on vacation.
Why talk about serious stuff?

00:38:16.185 --> 00:38:17.425
This calls for a celebration!

00:38:17.505 --> 00:38:20.065
- Come on.
- Two beers, please.

00:38:21.785 --> 00:38:22.705
The real deal.

00:38:22.785 --> 00:38:25.465
- And an opener too.
- You're so slow.

00:38:25.545 --> 00:38:28.465
Hey, not bad at all.

00:38:28.545 --> 00:38:30.665
- Of course.
- Do you drink often?

00:38:30.745 --> 00:38:32.025
Of course.

00:38:33.825 --> 00:38:35.225
Come on, cheers!

00:38:36.585 --> 00:38:37.985
You can do magic too?

00:38:57.625 --> 00:38:59.625
Seeing this reminds me of you.

00:38:59.705 --> 00:39:02.945
I still remember the first day we met.

00:39:03.025 --> 00:39:04.905
You said my life had no color.

00:39:06.505 --> 00:39:08.105
That was true.

00:39:08.185 --> 00:39:12.065
When you first arrived,
you didn't pay attention to anything.

00:39:12.145 --> 00:39:13.585
All you did was work.

00:39:13.665 --> 00:39:15.265
But now,

00:39:16.185 --> 00:39:18.865
I'm not the same anymore,

00:39:19.505 --> 00:39:21.665
ever since you came into my life.

00:39:24.105 --> 00:39:27.065
I'm insanely jealous of myself.

00:39:29.305 --> 00:39:34.465
I have a boyfriend
who's both cute and handsome.

00:39:36.425 --> 00:39:38.065
Which one should we pick?

00:39:41.145 --> 00:39:43.225
This one's pretty too.

00:39:48.105 --> 00:39:49.425
I'll take this one.

00:39:59.385 --> 00:40:04.825
From now on, I'll collect magnets with you
until our fridge is full.

00:40:04.905 --> 00:40:06.185
Then take just one.

00:40:06.985 --> 00:40:10.665
We still have many cases
to work on together.

00:40:10.745 --> 00:40:12.945
We'll be together until we're old.

00:40:13.025 --> 00:40:17.585
By then, our fridge will probably
be full of magnets already.

00:40:19.065 --> 00:40:22.065
If that happens, I'll buy another fridge.

00:40:22.145 --> 00:40:24.825
And if it's full again,
I'll buy another one.

00:40:28.585 --> 00:40:33.585
But it's nice to get a break
from work, isn't it?

00:40:34.545 --> 00:40:37.705
Grilled chicken here. Would you like some?

00:40:37.785 --> 00:40:39.505
Hot grilled chicken.

00:40:44.225 --> 00:40:46.265
One bag of sticky rice, please.

00:40:52.345 --> 00:40:56.185
Grilled chicken here. Would you like some?

00:40:56.265 --> 00:40:58.145
Grilled chicken here.

00:41:03.145 --> 00:41:06.185
I guess this isn't a vacation anymore.

00:41:07.345 --> 00:41:08.985
Yeah, I think so too.

00:41:10.385 --> 00:41:11.945
Let's go.

00:41:24.825 --> 00:41:25.865
ONE YEAR LATER

00:41:33.425 --> 00:41:35.185
Next time, no waterfalls.

00:41:35.265 --> 00:41:37.945
I played in the water
until my skin was all wrinkled.

00:41:39.105 --> 00:41:40.825
Really?

00:41:40.905 --> 00:41:44.145
- Let me see if that's true.
- Hey, pervert.

00:41:44.225 --> 00:41:46.145
Like I've never seen it before.

00:41:46.225 --> 00:41:48.345
I told you I didn't want to play.

00:41:48.425 --> 00:41:50.345
You're full of tricks.

00:41:50.425 --> 00:41:53.305
You pretended to drop something
and pretended to get a cramp.

00:41:53.385 --> 00:41:55.785
I jumped in to save you
because I was worried.

00:41:57.065 --> 00:42:00.105
Okay, Min.

00:42:00.705 --> 00:42:02.585
I'm sorry.

00:42:02.665 --> 00:42:03.865
Don't be mad.

00:42:04.825 --> 00:42:08.945
Let's think about
where we should go next instead.

00:42:10.185 --> 00:42:11.665
Where should we go?

00:42:12.345 --> 00:42:14.865
I don't want to go anywhere.
I want to work.

00:42:15.505 --> 00:42:19.425
- What?
- Try focusing on work, Captain.

00:42:19.505 --> 00:42:20.945
Maybe you'll get promoted
and replace me someday.

00:42:21.025 --> 00:42:23.985
Hey, Min.

00:42:24.745 --> 00:42:26.185
What's our house rule?

00:42:26.265 --> 00:42:28.945
No work talk at home.

00:42:30.985 --> 00:42:32.945
I'm just setting goals,

00:42:33.025 --> 00:42:35.745
so we can motivate each other at work.

00:42:35.825 --> 00:42:37.225
Okay?

00:42:38.545 --> 00:42:41.265
Tell me. Where do you want to travel?

00:42:42.905 --> 00:42:44.425
I don't know.

00:42:46.065 --> 00:42:47.665
As long as I'm with you, that's enough.

00:42:49.345 --> 00:42:51.785
You're such a sweet talker.

00:42:52.745 --> 00:42:55.225
Let me prove if it's really sweet.

00:43:08.265 --> 00:43:10.785
Egypt. That's a nice option.

00:43:10.865 --> 00:43:12.505
They just opened a new museum.

00:43:12.585 --> 00:43:14.345
I want to see the mummies.

00:43:15.305 --> 00:43:18.145
Haven't you seen enough
dead bodies at work already?

00:43:18.225 --> 00:43:21.385
Can you pick somewhere more romantic?

00:43:21.465 --> 00:43:22.945
Rome or Paris would be nice.

00:43:23.025 --> 00:43:24.425
The Maldives too.

00:43:24.505 --> 00:43:28.545
Then why bother randomizing it
if you're choosing anyway?

00:43:28.625 --> 00:43:30.545
I really can't read you.

00:43:32.025 --> 00:43:35.305
Then we'll have to stay together
for a long time

00:43:36.185 --> 00:43:37.905
until you can read me perfectly.

00:43:37.985 --> 00:43:39.025
That day might never come.

00:43:40.385 --> 00:43:41.745
I'm going.

00:43:43.865 --> 00:43:45.065
Hey, wait.

00:43:48.665 --> 00:43:49.625
What now?

00:43:52.825 --> 00:43:54.065
This.

00:44:16.745 --> 00:44:18.265
What are you doing?

00:44:19.865 --> 00:44:21.265
Give me a second.

00:44:22.585 --> 00:44:24.825
What's so hard about it? Let me try.

00:44:26.145 --> 00:44:28.105
See? It's not hard at all.

00:44:36.185 --> 00:44:37.745
Come on, I'll help you.

00:44:37.825 --> 00:44:39.545
Hold this.

00:44:57.785 --> 00:44:59.705
- Hello, Dr. Puth.
- Hello.

00:44:59.785 --> 00:45:02.225
You made it all the way here, bro? Bro.

00:45:02.305 --> 00:45:04.145
Seeing Sing's face, I switched right away.

00:45:04.225 --> 00:45:06.985
Spend your time guarding Jade instead.

00:45:07.065 --> 00:45:08.185
Jay.

00:45:09.225 --> 00:45:11.745
We still have to draft the contract.

00:45:12.345 --> 00:45:14.585
- Cut.
- There are no ghosts in this house.

00:45:15.945 --> 00:45:17.225
Jay!

00:45:17.305 --> 00:45:19.425
You told us you could do this.

00:45:19.505 --> 00:45:22.305
I know you're not scared.
I know you're not scared of the threat.

00:45:22.385 --> 00:45:24.985
Hey, that's too intense. That's too much.

00:45:25.065 --> 00:45:27.065
Cut.

00:45:28.665 --> 00:45:29.665
Done.

00:45:29.745 --> 00:45:30.865
We're filming. Keep running.

00:45:30.945 --> 00:45:32.305
Keep running. We're filming.

00:45:35.185 --> 00:45:37.625
I'm sorry. I couldn't hold it.

00:45:38.225 --> 00:45:39.785
- Look.
- Whoa!

00:45:39.865 --> 00:45:41.105
Hey, that's a bonus shot.

00:45:41.185 --> 00:45:42.625
Kamin, you broke character.

00:45:43.545 --> 00:45:44.465
I got carried away.

00:45:46.385 --> 00:45:47.945
Too much. Try again.

00:45:48.465 --> 00:45:50.265
- You've never wiped someone down, right?
- I'll just do it.

00:45:50.345 --> 00:45:52.705
It might not be perfect,
but it's full of love.

00:45:54.745 --> 00:45:57.265
You're totally out of character now.

00:45:57.345 --> 00:45:59.185
- I'm right here.
- Cut.